info.title: Mil-Equipment

assetID.description: Unique identifier of a serialised part.

atudControlNumber.description: A JAMES generated unique id for an ATUD based on Holding unit/date.

atudEndDate.description: The time and date that an 'Authority to use Document' (ATUD) was closed.

atudStartDate.description: The time and date that an 'Authority to use Document' (ATUD) was opened.

authServiceNumber.description: The service number of the person authorising the ATUD.

endODO.description: The usage recorded against the platform at ATUD_END_DATE(Primary usage counter only)

eventID.description: Unique identifier for a JAMES event (Usage of a vehicle/platform)

eventName.description: Assigned name fo the event.(Entered at event creation.)

eventOwnerName.description: The name of the unit to whom the platform belongs.

eventOwnerUIN.description: The unit identity number(UIN) of the platform ownder.

eventUsage.description: Difference between END_ODO and START_ODO (Primary usage counter only)

startODO.description: The usage recorded against the platform at ATUD_START_DATE(Primary usage counter only)

unitIdentityNumber.description: The unit identity number of the platform owner.(The unit it belongs too);

usageCounterType.description: The type of usage recorded agains the TAUD (Udually ODO- Odometer)

usageCounterUnit.description: The counter for the platform involved. Eg. Kilometers/Miles.
